-	829sqm* office accommodation over two levels 
-	Ground floor consists of multiple partitioned offices, workstations and amenities 
-	First floor consists of kitchen, meeting rooms, board rooms and open plan
-	Massive on site customer car park 
-	Close proximity to Brisbane Markets and Ipswich Road
